                <head>208. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d208fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Council, Institutional Files, Box 108, <gloss target="#t_SCC_1"
                            >SCC</gloss> 269, 02/06/80, Pakistan/Saudi Arabia. Secret. The meeting
                        took place in the White House Situation Room. The minutes are not attached
                        and were not found. <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1">Carter</persName> initialed
                        the first page.</note>
                </head>
